Look at their pupils.

13
00:03:47,240 --> 00:03:47,800
Lan Zhan,

14
00:03:49,160 --> 00:03:50,240
do you have any good solution?

15
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:51,440
Dash.

16
00:03:53,560 --> 00:03:57,040
Wait, wait, wait. Bro Lan. Bro Wei.

17
00:03:57,240 --> 00:03:58,080
Isn't it reckless

18
00:03:58,080 --> 00:03:59,520
