21
00:04:03,840 --> 00:04:05,375
Bro Wei, I really don't want to die.

22
00:04:05,375 --> 00:04:06,075
My canary...

23
00:04:11,120 --> 00:04:12,320
Listen. Bro Nie.

24
00:04:13,240 --> 00:04:14,240
Once we get out,

25
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:16,240
