26
00:04:16,760 --> 00:04:18,000
Don't let go of my hand, got it?

27
00:04:18,390 --> 00:04:20,000
Never let it go, understand?

28
00:07:20,360 --> 00:07:20,720
Let's go.

29
00:07:21,680 --> 00:07:22,800
Don't move!

30
00:07:26,560 --> 00:07:27,720
Don't move!

31
00:07:35,120 --> 00:07:35,400
She...

32
00:07:35,560 --> 00:07:37,480
Why does she appear again?

33
00:07:38,200 --> 00:07:40,613
You ignorant rushed into the Tiannv Temple.

34
00:07:40,613 --> 00:07:42,260
What punishment do you think you deserve?

35
00:07:42,920 --> 00:07:43,960
Don't punish us! Don't punish us!

36
00:07:44,080 --> 00:07:45,080
Wei Wuxian.

37
00:07:45,080 --> 00:07:46,425
You departed without permission.

38
00:07:46,425 --> 00:07:47,850
Do you plead guilty?

39
00:07:51,920 --> 00:07:52,600
Jiang Cheng,

40
00:07:53,120 --> 00:07:54,400
if you don't come out immediately,

41
00:07:55,080 --> 00:07:56,440
Lan Zhan will lose his temper.

42
00:08:03,000 --> 00:08:04,600
Why are you here, Jiang Cheng?

43
00:08:04,840 --> 00:08:05,960
You can come. Why can't I?

44
00:08:08,240 --> 00:08:10,400
It's fun to travel around all the way, isn't it?

45
00:08:11,000 --> 00:08:13,000
Without you harping on me,

46
00:08:13,200 --> 00:08:15,600
I am much more at ease.

47
00:08:15,800 --> 00:08:16,840
You have the nerve to say that?

48
00:08:16,960 --> 00:08:18,840
You just disappeared with a note left.

49
00:08:19,120 --> 00:08:20,040
Do you know how worried I...

50
00:08:22,320 --> 00:08:23,400
how worried my sister is?

51
00:08:24,000 --> 00:08:25,040
Bro Jiang.

52
00:08:25,240 --> 00:08:27,040
If you wanted to frighten Brother Wei, that's OK.

53
00:08:27,040 --> 00:08:28,800
Why did you even upset me and Bro Lan?

54
00:08:28,800 --> 00:08:29,400
We are...

55
00:08:31,240 --> 00:08:32,670
The silencing charm is lifted?

56
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:37,880
I'm upset for the journey to here because of you guys .

57
00:08:40,760 --> 00:08:42,280
All right, Jiang Cheng.

58
00:08:43,200 --> 00:08:44,840
It was me who wanted to follow Lanzhan.

59
00:08:45,600 --> 00:08:48,320
You can't blame him.

60
00:08:53,280 --> 00:08:55,480
I haven't blamed you yet. You're speaking for him.

61
00:08:56,280 --> 00:08:57,720
I don't know what you're going to do.

62
00:08:57,880 --> 00:08:59,880
But you have seen how dangerous it is.

63
00:09:00,320 --> 00:09:01,600
But for Miss Wen this time...

64
00:09:01,840 --> 00:09:02,680
Miss Wen?

65
00:09:03,240 --> 00:09:04,200
Wen Qing also has come here?

66
00:09:07,000 --> 00:09:07,440
Damn it.

67
00:09:08,480 --> 00:09:09,840
How long after the whistle stopped?

68
00:09:10,960 --> 00:09:12,360
I hope that Miss Wen is not in danger.

69
00:09:12,440 --> 00:09:13,160
Where is she now?

70
00:09:13,280 --> 00:09:14,520
Why do you come together?

71
00:09:27,760 --> 00:09:28,320
Miss Wen.

72
