73
00:09:43,280 --> 00:09:45,280
Is Wen Chao nearby?

74
00:09:45,760 --> 00:09:47,720
Why on earth does he want to kill us?

75
00:09:51,520 --> 00:09:53,040
Miss Wen, are you okay?

76
00:09:53,800 --> 00:09:54,680
Childe Jiang.

77
00:09:55,560 --> 00:09:57,080
Didn't I tell you to save them and leave?

78
00:09:57,200 --> 00:09:57,800
Miss Wen,

79
00:09:58,360 --> 00:09:59,560
