80
00:10:05,040 --> 00:10:06,800
They, they are coming again!

81
00:10:30,600 --> 00:10:31,360
You should leave now.

82
00:10:31,800 --> 00:10:32,560
Let's go together.

83
00:10:33,440 --> 00:10:34,240
I can't.

84
00:10:35,560 --> 00:10:37,360
Childe Jiang, you promised me.

85
00:10:37,520 --> 00:10:38,560
You would listen to me for coming here.

86
00:10:38,760 --> 00:10:39,920
Take them away quickly.

87
00:10:40,160 --> 00:10:41,680
You can't save them, Miss Wen.

88
00:10:41,840 --> 00:10:42,880
You should go before it's too late.

89
00:10:44,920 --> 00:10:45,800
You know how to save them?

90
00:10:46,920 --> 00:10:49,360
Doesn't the Dancing Peri extract people's spiritual cognition?

91
00:10:49,760 --> 00:10:50,560
They can be saved?

92
00:10:58,480 --> 00:10:59,040
Wen Qing.

93
00:10:59,360 --> 00:11:00,760
I don't care why you're here.

94
00:11:01,080 --> 00:11:02,720
But we're all stuck here right now.

95
00:11:03,160 --> 00:11:05,440
If we want to get out, we have to work together.

96
00:11:06,640 --> 00:11:09,240
If you know how to get them back to normal,

97
00:11:09,880 --> 00:11:11,560
I hope you can tell me now.

98
00:11:14,960 --> 00:11:15,440
Okay.

99
00:11:16,720 --> 00:11:17,600
I'll tell you.

100
00:11:19,320 --> 00:11:21,040
At present, they are not manipulated very well.

101
00:11:21,800 --> 00:11:23,240
Wen Chao only borrowed the power of Yin Iron

102
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:24,960
sealed on the Dire Owl by Wen Ruohan

103
00:11:24,960 --> 00:11:25,760
to control them.

104
00:11:27,440 --> 00:11:28,680
If you really want to help them,

105
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:30,160
kill the Dire Owl first.

106
00:11:31,880 --> 00:11:32,970
You should have told us earlier.

107
00:11:39,040 --> 00:11:41,200
Wei Ying, set up a Golden Silk Barrier to protect them.

108
00:11:50,040 --> 00:11:51,240
What are you doing? Wei Wuxian!

109
00:11:51,520 --> 00:11:53,920
Bro Wei, this won't last long.

110
00:11:54,040 --> 00:11:55,760
Do you want us dead?

111
00:11:56,160 --> 00:11:57,600
Jiang Cheng, you have the ability to protect them well.

112
00:11:57,960 --> 00:11:58,800
Take care of them.

113
00:11:58,880 --> 00:11:59,240
You...

114
00:11:59,680 --> 00:12:01,880
If it won't last, add a layer of protection.

115
00:12:02,160 --> 00:12:03,440
You're good at this.

116
00:12:03,520 --> 00:12:05,080
You must protect them well.

117
00:12:06,240 --> 00:12:08,040
I wanted to kill that owl long ago.

118
00:12:08,280 --> 00:12:09,000
Wait till we are back.

119
00:12:09,600 --> 00:12:10,240
Wait for us.

120
00:12:10,400 --> 00:12:11,120
Wei Wuxian!

121
00:12:12,680 --> 00:12:13,600
You bastard.

122
00:13:42,120 --> 00:13:42,760
Lan Zhan!

123
00:13:44,400 --> 00:13:45,360
Where are you, Lan Zhan?

124
00:13:47,880 --> 00:13:48,440
Lan Zhan!

125
00:13:51,760 --> 00:13:52,800
Where are you, Lan Zhan?

126
00:13:56,080 --> 00:13:56,640
Lan Zhan!

127
00:14:00,560 --> 00:14:01,080
Lan Zhan!

128
00:14:02,400 --> 00:14:04,160
What, what's going on?

129
00:14:06,040 --> 00:14:06,520
Listen.

130
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:27,760
What kind of a bird it is?

131
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:29,080
It's more astute than I am.

132
00:14:44,200 --> 00:14:44,840
Lan Zhan!

133
00:14:45,720 --> 00:14:46,680
Where are you, Lan Zhan?

134
00:14:49,280 --> 00:14:50,160
Not good. Not good. Not good.

135
00:14:51,240 --> 00:14:53,160
Was Lan Zhan caught by the Dire Owl?

136
00:14:54,360 --> 00:14:55,120
I'm next to you.

137
00:14:57,080 --> 00:14:58,680
You should have said something.

138
00:15:01,320 --> 00:15:03,600
The mist is brought by the hallucinations made by the Dire Owl.

139
00:15:04,400 --> 00:15:04,840
Don't worry.

140
00:15:05,440 --> 00:15:07,160
I can break it up with a Glitter Talisman.

141
00:15:23,120 --> 00:15:25,360
This hallucination can not only disorient people,

142
00:15:25,560 --> 00:15:26,520
but also disturb the mind.

143
00:15:27,160 --> 00:15:28,760
We can't concentrate at all now.

144
00:15:34,000 --> 00:15:34,840
That's strange.

145
00:15:35,480 --> 00:15:36,720
Why haven't you been disturbed?

146
00:15:37,880 --> 00:15:38,680
The Dire Owl's hallucination

147
00:15:38,800 --> 00:15:39,900
is the more disturbing

148
00:15:39,900 --> 00:15:41,175
the more thoughts you have in mind.

149
00:15:42,760 --> 00:15:45,320
Obviously, it is making use of my wisdom.

150
00:16:19,000 --> 00:16:19,520
Lan Zhan.

151
00:16:20,720 --> 00:16:21,280
Are you all right?

152
00:16:21,880 --> 00:16:22,400
Fine.

153
00:16:23,920 --> 00:16:25,160
Did you see who controled the bird?

154
00:16:25,600 --> 00:16:26,240
No.

155
00:16:41,120 --> 00:16:41,680
Wei Ying.

156
00:16:42,640 --> 00:16:43,600
Close the Five Senses.

157
00:17:03,080 --> 00:17:03,960
Fire-split Talisman.

158
00:17:36,280 --> 00:17:37,160
Wei Wuxian, you wretch.

159
00:17:37,240 --> 00:17:38,120
Come back quickly!

160
00:17:47,880 --> 00:17:49,720
Fortunately, my fan is made of the Darksteel.

161
00:17:49,840 --> 00:17:50,480
Otherwise...

162
00:17:51,320 --> 00:17:52,400
Get away from me!

163
00:17:52,400 --> 00:17:53,840
Bro Jiang, please help me mend this.

164
00:17:53,840 --> 00:17:55,000
It's worn out here.

165
00:17:55,000 --> 00:17:55,720
Make it up by yourself.

166
00:17:56,440 --> 00:17:57,320
But how?

167
00:18:12,920 --> 00:18:14,480
Miss Wen, come here.

168
00:18:14,560 --> 00:18:15,720
Help me mend here quickly.

169
00:18:24,040 --> 00:18:24,760
Miss Wen.

170
00:18:30,080 --> 00:18:30,800
Miss Wen.

171
00:18:31,080 --> 00:18:32,000
Don't get too close.

172
00:18:32,040 --> 00:18:33,240
Be careful that they will scratch you.

173
00:18:44,320 --> 00:18:45,080
Madam...

174
00:19:08,440 --> 00:19:08,880
Lan Zhan.

175
00:19:09,360 --> 00:19:10,360
It worked.

176
00:19:11,480 --> 00:19:12,040
Silent.

177
00:20:25,360 --> 00:20:26,880
How can you outsmart me?

178
00:20:35,440 --> 00:20:36,000
That was close.

179
00:20:36,320 --> 00:20:38,120
Lan Zhan, luckily, you come in time.

180
00:20:38,320 --> 00:20:39,360
Can you see who it is?

181
00:20:40,040 --> 00:20:41,240
The comer just sent part of his or her cognition.

182
00:20:41,600 --> 00:20:42,600
He or she didn't come in person.

183
00:20:45,160 --> 00:20:46,160
Good for him.

184
00:20:48,480 --> 00:20:49,953
Villagers' spiritual cognition has been returned.

185
00:20:50,000 --> 00:20:50,675
Let's go.

186
00:20:52,960 --> 00:20:53,560
Wait for me.

187
00:21:06,400 --> 00:21:08,000
Useless!

188
00:21:47,880 --> 00:21:48,360
Hello, Sir.

189
00:21:48,960 --> 00:21:49,960
Where are that three people just here?

190
00:21:51,560 --> 00:21:52,470
What?

191
00:21:53,320 --> 00:21:54,800
Where am I?

192
00:22:16,520 --> 00:22:18,480
I let Clan Leader Wen down.

193
00:22:18,920 --> 00:22:21,440
I almost hurt Qing.

194
00:22:21,600 --> 00:22:24,160
I'm good for nothing.

195
00:22:25,600 --> 00:22:26,160
Madam.

196
00:22:26,560 --> 00:22:27,240
Get up please.

197
00:22:28,560 --> 00:22:29,400
Get up, Madam.

198
00:22:30,760 --> 00:22:31,160
Come on.

199
00:22:35,600 --> 00:22:36,640
Qing.

200
00:22:37,160 --> 00:22:38,720
I'm sorry.

201
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:41,280
I'm of no use.

202
00:22:41,520 --> 00:22:42,240
Madam.

203
00:22:43,720 --> 00:22:44,760
Get up, everybody.

204
00:22:47,480 --> 00:22:48,080
Madam.

205
00:22:48,360 --> 00:22:49,560
Please don't say that.

206
00:22:50,240 --> 00:22:51,400
I should say sorry to you.

207
00:22:53,360 --> 00:22:54,520
You guys get out of here now.

208
00:22:54,720 --> 00:22:55,600
You can go anywhere

209
00:22:55,880 --> 00:22:56,760
except Qishan.

210
00:22:57,000 --> 00:22:58,200
And don't come back here again.

211
00:23:06,520 --> 00:23:07,240
Bro Jiang.

212
00:23:07,880 --> 00:23:10,920
Why do they know Miss Wen?

213
00:23:11,200 --> 00:23:12,000
And

214
00:23:12,360 --> 00:23:14,400
why did she bring us to the graveyard?

215
00:23:14,800 --> 00:23:15,600
How should I know?

216
00:23:17,440 --> 00:23:18,240
Jiang Cheng.

217
00:23:19,320 --> 00:23:20,160
Miss Wen.

218
00:23:20,880 --> 00:23:22,560
Bro Wei, we are here.

219
00:23:27,600 --> 00:23:28,160
Bro Wei.

220
00:23:28,520 --> 00:23:30,600
I knew you could kill the Dire Owl.

221
00:23:30,760 --> 00:23:32,440
You are really as sharp as a razor.

222
00:23:39,920 --> 00:23:40,600
But

223
00:23:41,320 --> 00:23:42,480
why are you here?

224
00:23:49,200 --> 00:23:49,880
Miss Wen.

225
00:23:50,425 --> 00:23:53,325
What on earth is this place?

226
00:23:58,360 --> 00:24:00,750
This is where my clan was buried.

227
00:24:08,520 --> 00:24:09,880
So that ancestral temple...

228
00:24:10,800 --> 00:24:11,360
You're right.

229
00:24:12,880 --> 00:24:14,080
That's Wen clan's ancestral temple.

230
00:24:15,280 --> 00:24:17,240
We are a collateral branch of Wen clan of Qishan

231
00:24:17,560 --> 00:24:18,600
specializing in medicine.

232
00:24:19,080 --> 00:24:22,040
After leaving Qishan, we live here for generations.

233
00:24:23,720 --> 00:24:24,760
But unexpectedly,

234
00:24:26,040 --> 00:24:27,560
a disaster suddenly happened here.

235
00:24:50,880 --> 00:24:51,920
Father!

236
00:25:00,840 --> 00:25:01,960
Qing, go!

237
00:25:12,750 --> 00:25:14,070
As for the blood of our branch,

238
00:25:14,960 --> 00:25:16,280
we are the last few.

239
00:25:17,280 --> 00:25:19,560
Was it because Dancing Peri extracts the spiritual cognition?

240
00:25:19,880 --> 00:25:20,480
Yes.

241
00:25:22,040 --> 00:25:22,960
Since then

242
00:25:23,760 --> 00:25:26,040
Wen Ning and I were brought up by His Excellency

243
00:25:27,120 --> 00:25:28,040
back in Qishan.

244
00:25:28,320 --> 00:25:30,760
But why the Dancing Peri hurt people suddenly?

245
00:25:31,720 --> 00:25:32,520
I don't know.

246
00:25:44,680 --> 00:25:45,080
Father.

247
00:25:45,880 --> 00:25:47,880
I could have snatched up Wei Wuxian and his fellows.

248
00:25:48,400 --> 00:25:50,440
It was because of the ignorance of Wen Qing.

249
00:25:50,840 --> 00:25:52,280
She should dare to stop me secretly.

250
00:25:52,400 --> 00:25:53,080
You fool!

251
00:25:54,240 --> 00:25:56,720
Those who lived in Dafan Mountain are Wen Qing's people.

252
00:25:57,120 --> 00:25:57,880
If you hadn't used

253
00:25:57,880 --> 00:25:59,720
the power of Yin Iron I sealed in the Dire Owl

254
00:25:59,800 --> 00:26:01,040
making them into puppets,

255
00:26:01,280 --> 00:26:03,160
Wen Qing wouldn't have stopped you.

256
00:26:04,080 --> 00:26:06,200
Besides, I asked you to help Xue Yang.

257
00:26:06,320 --> 00:26:08,400
Why did you act on your own and stop them?

258
00:26:10,680 --> 00:26:11,760
You are right, father.

259
00:26:12,360 --> 00:26:13,160
I'm sorry.

260
00:26:15,360 --> 00:26:16,840
Go and find Yin Iron back.

261
00:26:17,720 --> 00:26:19,920
This time you should make no mistake.

262
00:26:20,120 --> 00:26:21,480
Yes, father.

263
00:26:32,920 --> 00:26:35,440
I hope things won't go wrong any more.

264
00:26:36,440 --> 00:26:37,680
If you stay with me,

265
00:26:38,240 --> 00:26:39,920
I'm sure you can remain unscathed.

266
00:26:40,280 --> 00:26:41,560
Do not boast yourself.

267
00:26:41,880 --> 00:26:43,520
If Miss Wen didn't come to Dafan Mountain,

268
00:26:43,640 --> 00:26:44,920
can you still be alive?

269
00:26:46,920 --> 00:26:47,920
Staying with you

270
00:26:47,960 --> 00:26:49,200
