271
00:26:50,360 --> 00:26:51,080
Jiang Cheng.

272
00:26:51,850 --> 00:26:54,130
Now that you think I bring you misfortune,

273
00:26:54,920 --> 00:26:56,240
why did you follow me?

274
00:26:56,400 --> 00:26:56,880
I...

275
00:27:01,960 --> 00:27:03,240
