276
00:27:03,440 --> 00:27:04,640
In order to cross Dafan Mountain

277
00:27:04,880 --> 00:27:05,760
there's only one road.

278
00:27:06,640 --> 00:27:07,960
I'd like to say you are following me.

279
00:27:13,520 --> 00:27:15,320
The barred rock chicken.

280
00:27:23,560 --> 00:27:24,400
Look at that!

281
00:27:25,880 --> 00:27:26,560
There!

282
00:27:26,640 --> 00:27:28,680
How does it know I am hungry?

283
00:27:29,360 --> 00:27:30,000
Bro Wei.

284
00:27:30,800 --> 00:27:32,560
We two can catch it from front and back.

285
00:27:33,920 --> 00:27:34,440
